	(6288,2198,'_mcb-products','[xt_divider style=\"shadow\"]\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/olde-froth.png\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-2404\" alt=\"olde-froth\" src=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/olde-froth.png\" width=\"58\" height=\"163\" /></a>Olde Frothingslosh</h3>\r\nAdmired by all, worn by the lucky few– the mustache is the universal symbol for a sophisticated man (and a courageous woman). Unfortunately no beer could match the raw manhood, power, or responsibility that comes with a well-dressed upper lip––until now. Certified to fit any shape of glass, Olde Frothingslosh is a smooth medium-body lager with a hint of bitterness and an exquisite sense of facial hair. This beer goes down easy with a clean, sharp flavor, and entices the nose with a mild citrusy aroma.\r\n\r\nabv : 4.7%'),
