	(6440,2202,'_mcb-products','<span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">[xt_divider style=\"shadow\"]</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"font-size: 15px; font-weight: bold;\"><a href=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/american-light.png\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-2406\" alt=\"american-light\" src=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/american-light.png\" width=\"58\" height=\"163\" /></a>American Light</span>\r\n\r\nThere’s nothing like tasting the glory of American Light after a hard day’s work. Instilled with American pride in every sip, this easy drinking light beer captures the rich heritage of our homeland and delivers a dependable and refreshing taste. Brewed for Americans by Americans, American Light is a great classic and an even better value.\r\n\r\nabv : 4.2%'),
